Package helpers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColorConstants
    This class provides the Colors specifically referenced and copied by gui.mainpage.MainPageFiller and gui.popup.PopupFiller, though they are used in most of the GUI classes through parameter-passing by gui.mainpage.MainPageFiller and gui.popup.PopupFiller.
    FontConstants
    This class provides the Fonts specifically referenced and copied by gui.mainpage.MainPageFiller and gui.popup.PopupFiller, though they are used in most of the GUI classes through parameter-passing by gui.mainpage.MainPageFiller and gui.popup.PopupFiller.
